hackathon-description-text: MLH Local Hack Day brought to you by UB ACM. Students will submit their semester long projects!
hackathon-eligibility: University at Buffalo students who are a part of UB ACM (ubacm.org)
hackathon-requirements: You must have worked on this throughout the Fall Semester.
hackathon-rules:
You are allowed to submit projects you've worked on throught the Fall 2017 semester.
You must be a part of UB ACM and a UB student. (ubacm.org).

hackathon-prizes.prize-content: Points cannot be exchanged for money.

hackathon-description-header: Empowering UB students to create, learn, and submit their semester long projects!
